text: Young Communist League of Sweden or Sveriges Kommunistiska Ungdomsförbund may refer to: * Young Left (Sweden), formerly known as Sveriges Kommunistiska Ungdomsförbund 1921-1958 * Young Communist League of Sweden (1977), a youth wing founded in 1977 by the Arbetarpartiet Kommunisterna (APK) * Young Communist League of Sweden (2000), a youth wing founded in 2000 by the Communist Party of Sweden (the successor of APK)
title: Young Communist League of Sweden
